Changes for R-package grainsize

Version 0.1.0 (2014-10-20)
	- Initial version

Version 0.1.1 (2015-01-16)
	- Function read.CamSizerXT() added
	- Output format of read.LA950() modified
	- examples homogenised

Version 0.1.2 (2015-08-23)
	- Function calc_mean added
	- all function names homogenised
	- all code switched to ROxygen2 format

Version 0.1.3 (2017-05-09)
	- Function read_LA950 rewritten for new data format
	- a set of bugs removed
	- read_LA950(): output structure changed, meta contains complete results

